B2AUD.original: ~z~We get caught and everyone will be coming after us.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~一旦被抓，所有人都会盯上我们。

B2AUD.original: ~z~Looks like we're gonna have to do this the old fashioned way. Get these commies, Niko.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~看起来我们只好走老路了。干掉这群共党，Niko。

B2AUD.original: ~z~That truck was part of the plan. You start cutting corners and you get sloppy. See you round.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~那辆卡车是计划的一部分。欲速则不达啊。回头见。

B2AUD.original: ~z~Shit, if anyone does start listening to Ray's shit then I could be in some trouble.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，要是真有人信Ray说的那套，我就会有麻烦了。

B2AUD.original: ~z~This is it, keep a cool head and everything should be fine.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~就这里，头脑不要发热，应该就没问题。

B2AUD.original: ~z~Hey, buddy, we're here to pick up the shipment.
~z~I'm paranoid because we especially don't wanna get caught on this one.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~我是有点多疑，因为这次我们绝对不能被抓。

B2AUD.original: ~z~His moves might be easy for you to see, but maybe they're working.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~他的举动可能是很容易被你看穿，但说不定确实管用。

B2AUD.original: ~z~No. I do some work for him.
~z~Tell him I went out to get some fresh air.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~跟他讲我出去呼吸新鲜空气去了。

B2AUD.original: ~z~Family's a way of saying we ain't gonna fuck each other... at least that's what it's meant to mean.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~家族只是说我们不会内斗而已...至少说起来是这样。

B2AUD.original: ~z~The Feds'll throw away the key, the Russians and the Ancelottis'll know we was fucking them over.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~政府会判我们无期，俄国人和Ancelotti家族会知道是我们捣的鬼。

B2AUD.original: ~z~He's got his eyes on my position, the skipper's too, I'm sure. Wanting it and getting are two different things though.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~他觊觎我的位置，还觊觎老大的位置，真的。想要跟得到是两码事。

B2AUD.original: ~z~We're heading to the docks in North Holland. Move out.
~z~Hey man, this familiarity is getting to me. I'm a 'friend' of Ray's. I'm part of the 'family'.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~嘿，兄弟，这亲戚攀的就有点过分了啊。~n~说我是Ray的「朋友」，说我是「家族」的一份子。

B2AUD.original: ~z~For the record, I did everything I was meant to do.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~本人声明，我分内的事我都做到了。

B2AUD.original: ~z~Hey Phil, that's got to be the last of them.
~z~If someone who knew what I knew got flipped then the whole organization would go down.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~要是知道的跟我一样多的人反水了，整个组织都会倒掉。

B2AUD.original: ~z~Taking a shipment of coke from some Russians before they can sell it to the Ancelottis.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~在俄国人把可卡因卖给Ancelotti家族前抢走这批货。

B2AUD.original: ~z~It should be a lot of sugar, but that ain't the only reason why we're taking this truck.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~拉的应该是糖，不过开这辆车也不止这一个原因。

B2AUD.original: ~z~-seven horse, seven race, Joe Shmoe.~n~-Hey Phil.
~z~Yeah, well, maybe you're right. Maybe you ain't. I dunno.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~行，好吧，你说的可能有理，也可能不对。我不知道。

B2AUD.original: ~z~Keep your head, things ain't even started yet. What're we doing?
B2AUD.translated: ~z~保持冷静，都没开始办正事呢。待会儿怎么做？

B2AUD.original: ~z~I think we got the cocaine to ourselves now, Phil.
~z~Ray's a greedy rat. He wants this stuff more than anyone else, but that don't mean he's gonna get it.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~Ray是个贪婪的小人。他比谁都想得到这批货，但他未必就能得到。

B2AUD.original: ~z~Why we need this truck? It must be a shit load of coke we're taking?
B2AUD.translated: ~z~要这辆卡车干嘛？我们肯定要拉一大堆可卡因吧？

B2AUD.original: ~z~It's gonna take more than wanting it real bad. It's gonna take a clear head.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~光是想要还不够，还需要清醒的头脑。

B2AUD.original: ~z~We just got the heads up that a shipment has arrived in Liberty City by boat.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~我们刚收到消息，有批货用船运进了自由城。

B2AUD.original: ~z~That coke's lost. It's lost to us, man. Later.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~可卡因没了，被我们弄没了，兄弟。回见。

B2AUD.original: ~z~Ok listen. There's a truck waiting for us. It's under the overpass off Catskill Avenue, drive us there.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~听着。我们要去开一辆卡车，车在Catskill大道的高架下面，带我过去。

B2AUD.original: ~z~You know something? I woulda liked Ray to be on this job instead of me. But there's some things that he ain't trusted with.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~你知道吗？这次的活我更想让Ray替我。不过他有他不被信任的原因。

B2AUD.original: ~z~Ah shit, it's three days early, Madonna mia, what am I gonna do?
B2AUD.translated: ~z~啊，干！提前了三天，我的天哪，这我怎么办？

B2AUD.original: ~z~Hell, our own family might come after us for fear we'll turn state's.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，就连我们的家族都可能派人灭我们的口，以防背叛。

B2AUD.original: ~z~Since that little love affair ended, they been getting this Russian guy to supply them with C.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~那段感情结束后，他们就找这些俄国人进可卡因了。

B2AUD.original: ~z~Whether you're putting yourself in harm's way because that's the way the Skipper wants it done,
B2AUD.translated: ~z~老大叫你当敢死队送死，你也只能照办。

B2AUD.original: ~z~Me neither. Maybe if we want it more than anyone else, we'll be able to hang onto it.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~我也不想。或许只要我们比谁都想得到它，就能弄到手。

B2AUD.original: ~z~I'll take the one on the right, you get the one on the left. C'mon, move it, Niko!
B2AUD.translated: ~z~我开右边那艘，你开左边那艘。赶紧，走吧，Niko！

B2AUD.original: ~z~You was helping those Irish idiots cause some beef between the Ancellotis and their Albanian muscle a while back.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~之前你帮那些爱尔兰白痴破坏了Ancelotti家族和阿尔巴尼亚打手间的关系。

B2AUD.original: ~z~Then we drive away, no questions asked.
~z~Enough governments have let me down in the past. I don't know why I'd trust this one.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~过去让我失望的政府已经够多了，怎么会相信这里这个。

B2AUD.original: ~z~I'll see you at the docks in North Holland, Niko.
~z~I'll get the jobs done if the money is there, and I ain't gonna turn state's.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~只要钱到位，我就能完成工作，我也不会背叛。

B2AUD.original: ~z~We should be able to turn up and have 'em load it up for us.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~我们应该能直接进去等他们过来装货。

B2AUD.original: ~z~That's the plan. Whether it works or not remains to be seen.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~计划如此。能否成功有待实践。

B2AUD.original: ~z~We're taking a load of product off of some Russians the Ancelottis have been dealing with.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~我们要从最近跟Ancelotti家族做生意的俄国人那里偷一批货。

B2AUD.original: ~z~there ain't that much control in anything.
~z~or you're staying away from your kids because of a stupid court order and a malicious bitch of an ex-wife;
B2AUD.translated: ~z~被恶毒的前妻告上法庭，也只能服从白痴判决就此告别亲生子女。

B2AUD.original: ~z~I work in waste management. Everything we're saying is fiction, it has no bearing in the real world. Watch it Niko.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~我在垃圾处理厂工作。我们说的一切纯属虚构，与真实世界无关。注意点，Niko。

B2AUD.original: ~z~Err, Niko. The stuff's still on those boats. We best get 'em outta here.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~呃，Niko。货还在船上，最好直接把船开走。

B2AUD.original: ~z~Hey, amigo, let's make this easy. I just wanna give the stuff to my boss and go home.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~嘿，大兄弟，咱们省点事吧。我只想把货交给老大，然后回家。

B2AUD.original: ~z~You're gonna learn that there ain't much in this life that you got control of.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~你会明白生活中很少有你能掌控的事情的。

B2AUD.original: ~z~Well a lot of people want to get hold of this merchandise as well.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~其实也有很多人想弄到这次这批货。

B2AUD.original: ~z~I been around long enough to know that there is some things that we don't have a choice about,
B2AUD.translated: ~z~来这儿这么久，我也知道有些事大家都没得选，

B2AUD.original: ~z~For the record I don't know what this man is talking about. We're rehearsing a scene for an acting class.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~本人声明，我不知道这个人在说什么。我们是在排练表演课的片段。

B2AUD.original: ~z~Exactly. We're taking the C off the Russians so they can't deliver it to the Ancelottis.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~正是。我们从俄国人那儿抢走可卡因，他们就没法给Ancelotti家族送货了。

B2AUD.original: ~z~Man, they ain't giving up easy. We got more of them!
B2AUD.translated: ~z~天哪，他们还是不肯放弃。追兵过来了！

B2AUD.original: ~z~You're the boss, it ain't like I'm working for free.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~你是老板，我好像也不是白干。

B2AUD.original: ~z~You ain't gonna be happy about everything you get told to do, are ya?
B2AUD.translated: ~z~别人吩咐你做的事哪有能让你满意的。

B2AUD.original: ~z~Anyways, excuse me if I wanna be absolutely sure that we got our asses covered.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~总之，恕我太过在意我们的安全。

B2AUD.original: ~z~Some of my boys stole it from the Ancelottis this morning.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~今早我手下的人从Ancelotti家族那儿偷的车。

B2AUD.original: ~z~Too many people wanted that ice, no one was ever going to end up with it.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~太多人盯着钻石了，没人能拿着它善终。

B2AUD.original: ~z~No, you ain't. I ain't either. That's why we gotta at least try what we're told to do.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~对，不白干，我也一样。所以怎么说都得照命令来一次。

B2AUD.original: ~z~We're taking this C to the docks in North Holland. Come on.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~把这批货送到North Holland的码头。快点。

B2AUD.original: ~z~They're gonna let us take the coke with this truck then, are they?
B2AUD.translated: ~z~他们会让我们开着卡车就把可卡因带走吗？

B2AUD.original: ~z~Shit, you sound like you're saying all this just so it's clear on the wire tap.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~我靠，你这种说话方式像是特意说给窃听器听的。

B2AUD.original: ~z~All I care about is that you're loyal enough to get the jobs done and not turn state's.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~我只关心你能否忠诚地完成工作，并且不会背叛。

B2AUD.original: ~z~That's what the talk about the docks was?
~z~We lost some of that sugar, it ain't no good taking it from the Russians if we can't sell it ourselves. Ciao.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~我们损失了一些糖。要是卖不出去，不就白从俄国人那儿抢了吗。再见。

B2AUD.original: ~z~There's something wrong about you. Get out of the truck real slow.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~你们不太对劲。慢慢从车上下——来。

B2AUD.original: ~z~No, but we can be pretty sure it's clean. Chill out.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~没，但这车肯定没装东西。放松点。

B2AUD.original: ~z~That wasn't a successful operation by any way you look at it.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~怎么看都不是一次成功的行动。

B2AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, sure, this is just plan A. It's the one Jimmy P worked out.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~对，确实，这只是A计划。是Jimmy P想出来的。

B2AUD.original: ~z~Fuck you, I ain't. I just keep thinking these choppers is following me, that's all.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~去你妈的，不是。只是我经常觉得有直升机跟着，就这样。

B2AUD.original: ~z~Sure, sure, I get that. Whatever makes it all make sense in your head.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~好，好，我明白了。只要你觉得舒服就行。

B2AUD.original: ~z~Because these is the orders and we gotta follow them. That's the way things work.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~因为这是必须服从的命令。规矩就是如此。

B2AUD.original: ~z~And we make some money in the process by selling the stuff. Easy.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~我们还能顺便把货卖了赚钱。简单。

B2AUD.original: ~z~I don't let anyone in here until I get the word.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~接到指示之前，谁也别想过去。

B2AUD.original: ~z~It's the one the Russians is expecting to come pick up the C.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~给俄国人装货的卡车就是这辆。

B2AUD.original: ~z~By your logic that means it's going to end up dissolving into the Humboldt River.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~照你说的，这批货全得溶解在Humboldt河里。

B2AUD.original: ~z~I ain't part of no family. I'm an independent contractor.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~才不是什么家族成员。我就一民间杀手。

B2AUD.original: ~z~And that means that certain people is gonna assume we'll rat.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~而且还会有人怀疑我们泄密换取减刑。

B2AUD.original: ~z~The Feds monitoring my every move. I flip out whenever I'm even outside.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~FIB监控我的一举一动。每次出门我都很紧张。

B2AUD.original: ~z~It's all internet porn and dreamin about home, that ain't no life.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~只能看看黄色网站，奢望能够回家，那才不是生活。

B2AUD.original: ~z~So, why don't we use a more subtle approach, not just drive right into the middle of them?
B2AUD.translated: ~z~那我们干嘛不换种更稳妥的方案？非得直接开进去吗？

B2AUD.original: ~z~You mean that someone in the family would see someone else going inside as an opportunity to get ahead?
B2AUD.translated: ~z~就是说有些家族成员会把别人被抓视为上升机会？

B2AUD.original: ~z~I'm hoping that this endeavor is gonna be more fruitful.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~希望这次的付出能更有回报一些。

B2AUD.original: ~z~Sounds straightforward. We take the coke so that the Russians and the Ancelottis have a falling out.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~听起来很简单。我们偷走可卡因，俄国人和Ancelotti家族间就破裂了。

B2AUD.original: ~z~Damn, looks like these guys really want to hold onto the coke!
B2AUD.translated: ~z~我靠，看来他们真的不肯对这些可卡因放手！

B2AUD.original: ~z~And it don't help that not everyone in the organization is pulling in the same direction.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~而组织里的人也不是团结一心的。

B2AUD.original: ~z~I don't think I'd trust him to send me on another job after the shit he had me doing.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~就凭他让我做的那些事，我都不敢让他再给我一份活干。

B2AUD.original: ~z~Shit man, I'm just the hired help. I'm the fucking immigrant maid cleaning up your guys' shit.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~我靠，老兄，我就是个拿钱办事的，就一给你们收拾烂摊子的移民女仆。

B2AUD.original: ~z~Niko, it looks like we're gonna have to do this the old fashioned way.
~z~You and me know it ain't gonna work.
~z~I'm gonna have to take a chance with you, pal.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~我只能跟你碰碰运气了，兄弟。

B2AUD.original: ~z~I don't know if anyone would give away a load of coke without asking any questions.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~我是不觉得会有人不加怀疑就交出一大堆可卡因。

B2AUD.original: ~z~There ain't no action and the only cannolis you're gonna see are the ones on TV.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~那里什么都不会发生，只能在电视上见到意大利卷饼。

B2AUD.original: ~z~Alright, alright. It's just that if we get caught on this one, you and me is going down for a long time.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~好吧，好吧。万一这回被抓，我们就得牢底坐穿了。

B2AUD.original: ~z~Whacking someone who catches some heavy time is just an insurance policy.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~暗杀被判重刑的人只是一道保险措施。

B2AUD.original: ~z~After all of that, you guys didn't even get the diamonds.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~事干了不少，结果钻石都没拿到。

B2AUD.original: ~z~I'm a grown man walking around like a chump.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~我这么大人了，还跟白痴一样到处跑。

B2AUD.original: ~z~You're working with the wrong people if you expect 'em to whack you if you go inside.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~你要是觉得进去了会有人暗杀你，那说明你入错伙了。

B2AUD.original: ~z~Phil, there's more of these guys coming after us.
~z~I didn't pick you for a helicopter enthusiast.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~没想到你还是直升机爱好者啊。

B2AUD.original: ~z~Every move he makes is so obvious, it's disgusting to see him trying to sleaze his way up the ladder.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~他那些举动的意图太明显了，谋求高位的样子实在是让人想吐。

B2AUD.original: ~z~You handled yourself real good back there. Kept your head. That's a valuable trait.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~你刚才的表现很好，头脑冷静。很可贵的品质。

B2AUD.original: ~z~Shit, you seen any choppers? Any birds been in the sky?
B2AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，有见着直升机吗？天上有在飞的吗？

B2AUD.original: ~z~It's the boss... said you gotta head down the docks... emergency... said you'd understand.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~是老大...他要你立刻去码头...情况紧急...说你听得懂。

B2AUD.original: ~z~He talks a lot of shit, but he's a good earner, capiche?
B2AUD.translated: ~z~他是很会扯，但确实特能赚钱，懂吗？

B2AUD.original: ~z~The problem was Ray's planning and the amount of people involved.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~问题出在Ray的计划和牵涉到的人数上。

B2AUD.original: ~z~but there's other times where you got to look at something and make a decision for yourself.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~但也有需要你仔细审视自己决定的时候。

B2AUD.original: ~z~Then, they ship you off to Ohio and get you selling microwaves.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~然后就送你到俄亥俄州，让你去卖微波炉。

B2AUD.original: ~z~And that the only way we're gonna be able to leave that place with the sugar is if all the Russians in there are dead.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~唯一能拉着糖出来的情况，就是在场的俄国人都死了。

B2AUD.original: ~z~I can't follow every order I'm given.
~z~Shit Niko, what we meant to do with a boat on dry land?
~z~Maybe he's getting somewhere. He definitely knows a lot of people.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~也许他能攀上高枝，毕竟他认识的人多。

B2AUD.original: ~z~the thing about Ray is he's a good earner.
~z~Even Russian coke runners ain't that stupid.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~就算是俄国毒贩子也没那么蠢。

B2AUD.original: ~z~Tommy, gimme a call if my big buddy calls.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~Tommy，要是老大找我，给我打个电话。

B2AUD.original: ~z~These guys promise you a new life if you screw every person who ever did a kind thing for you.
B2AUD.translated: ~z~这些人说是只要出卖所有帮过你的人，就会给你新的生活。
